c: 43
v: 49
t: "wqal fireawn wmlwh lmwsa: ya 'ayuha alealam (wkan alsaahir fihim ezymana yuaqqirwnh walam yakun alsihr sifat dhm) ade lana rabak bieahdih aldhy eahid 'iilayk wama khssak bih min alfdayl 'an yakshif eanaa aledhab, fa'iina kashf eanaa aleadhab fa'iinana lamuhtadun muwminun bima jitana bh"